
    HEAD
	Animations: -, Cry, Attack
	Hook point: torso
	Will usually face the target


    TORSO
	Animations: -, Cry, MeleeAttack(s), Run, RangeAttack(s), whatever
	Hook point: legs
	Point0: HeadHookPoint
	Point1 (directional): RightHandHookPoint
	Point2 (directional): LeftHandHookPoint
	Armor hooked between 0 and HeadHookPoint.


    CYCLE
	Animations: -, Attack, Die
	Hook point: torso


    LEGS
	Animations: -, Walk, Run, SupportFwd, SupportBwd, SupportMid
	Hook point: ground
	Point 0: TorsoHookPoint

